{"tid":1238664,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳鈺琪祝緒丹都比下去？　19歲李蘭迪被喻「最美古裝女星」","createTime":"2019-06-18T01:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T11:20:20.000Z","uid":173631,"like":1,"dislike":146,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"579cbba27b482c1cdea6508f71735abd137fec2c","tid":1238664,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918202/org/621e02edc8dc37e51b3158f294716e14.jpg/wInRegH3ozuwZiB_wg54BLzOb7WIWBQfHdAWzB3QFsw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918202%2Forg%2F621e02edc8dc37e51b3158f294716e14.jpg%2FwInRegH3ozuwZiB_wg54BLzOb7WIWBQfHdAWzB3QFsw&h=bdb7f8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然早前微博發起的「古裝四美」票選大賽已經圓滿結束，而結果亦由有「中國4千年一遇美女」封號的鞠婧禕擊敗一眾前輩榮登榜首，就連近日憑內地劇集《倚天屠龍記》而人氣急升的陳鈺琪（飾趙敏）以及祝緒丹（飾周芷若）都不敵。但最近內又再有內地網民力捧另一「新」星為「最美古裝女星」，鞠婧禕的榜首位到底能否坐得穩妥？<br />\n<br />\n重溫一下十大「最美古裝劇女星」（順次序排列）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918197/org/4b28642878764a9076e21d96806fa35d.jpg/nY_QlmirRZ8TkQkBxl_SBPgwuy_iRH9byWM6C8ljOgs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918197%2Forg%2F4b28642878764a9076e21d96806fa35d.jpg%2FnY_QlmirRZ8TkQkBxl_SBPgwuy_iRH9byWM6C8ljOgs&h=39f12bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918196/org/2d07e35901a4f2d0f9719b049cc4dc61.jpg/i0l6LSLk8JDuuamTCmOTpteqJymm8mCRN4SGtDeEhrQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918196%2Forg%2F2d07e35901a4f2d0f9719b049cc4dc61.jpg%2Fi0l6LSLk8JDuuamTCmOTpteqJymm8mCRN4SGtDeEhrQ&h=56f725ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918198/org/decf538f77858ecb6fff7a3771d60709.jpg/cnO_3AiDxJV72-3TrmQ64WiaAqgCoP93PvtlGT77ZRk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918198%2Forg%2Fdecf538f77858ecb6fff7a3771d60709.j