ges/2918204/org/efef6d53c7e22cadd3cf95a5c68eda2e.jpg/pR1TSup5zhbsvNKM8ADO20BiTOgz-HGl3AtPIdwLTyE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918204%2Forg%2Fefef6d53c7e22cadd3cf95a5c68eda2e.jpg%2FpR1TSup5zhbsvNKM8ADO20BiTOgz-HGl3AtPIdwLTyE&h=7401a77a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918203/org/687573add6b4aed6ed61d7e4e7fd9548.jpg/E3M5p05JXmzHimT81yzVCZJZk_jwUps7CbvGOgm7xjo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918203%2Forg%2F687573add6b4aed6ed61d7e4e7fd9548.jpg%2FE3M5p05JXmzHimT81yzVCZJZk_jwUps7CbvGOgm7xjo&h=37b47162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918223/org/7913250c057ba7a836aa1b83d25a9995.jpg/STK6zrVFRvGDr2XHl7J6X3bMPYwrlvI9gjXRiII10Yg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918223%2Forg%2F7913250c057ba7a836aa1b83d25a9995.jpg%2FSTK6zrVFRvGDr2XHl7J6X3bMPYwrlvI9gjXRiII10Yg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=87332502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李蘭迪而家係「上海唐人電影製作有限公司」旗下藝人，係古力娜扎嘅師妹！曾經演過《無心法師II》。（劇照）<br />\n19歲李蘭迪原來係天才？<br />\n<br />\n被網友力捧的「新」星，正是這位年僅19歲的李蘭迪。其實她早於10年前出道，當年只得10歲的她在電影《愛你輸給了誰》就開始涉足電影圈。2016年，她更憑電影《少年棋王》在「青海西寧環保兒童電影展」中獲得「最具潛力兒童女演員奬」。雖然在過去十年間，李蘭迪參與過愈20部電影／劇集作品，但她同時亦沒有荒廢學業，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">去年在中國高考中以總分466分成為全國第二名。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>早前李蘭迪、陳鈺琪以及祝緒丹獲邀到節目《創造營2019》擔任助演嘉賓，李蘭迪的人氣絕不遜於兩位姐姐！<br />\n<br />\n《創造營2019》：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918226/org/3d1ea22b652457e85af3b7807ccca206.jpg/QrAU0tf-R9MUH7QMQl8Mh41yZMYMR9a6TnbOY052zmM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918226%2Forg%2F3d1ea22b652457e85af3b7807ccca206.jpg%2FQrAU0tf-R9MUH7QMQl8Mh41yZMYMR9a6TnbOY052zmM&h=c47443e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918225/org/a9bdba73182e5ef452a072126372f8b0.jpg/tpR1qcsulM1anTUPO9COLe3LUxO_e0y_XsijLF7Ioyw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918225%2Forg%2Fa9bdba73182e5ef452a072126372f8b0.jpg%2FtpR1qcsulM1anTUPO9COLe3LUxO_e0y_XsijLF7Ioyw&h=6a0917a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918227/org/a672d42cddab0d517b06ceaef1dd3b6a.jpg/0EEgIW-my51Mz3KDcPFwkondlM5dyUCoYlF9NmJRfTY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918227%2Forg%2Fa672d42cddab0d517b06ceaef1dd3b6a.jpg%2F0EEgIW-my51Mz3KDcPFwkondlM5dyUCoYlF9NmJRfTY&h=90444f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918229/org/e263385dfd1718eb8f3adf4db09285f2.jpg/7FBNsaFJUU9TJzepErDrLITQfcmqBMo-slCbfbJQm30\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918229%2Forg%2Fe263385dfd1718eb8f3adf4db09285f2.jpg%2F7FBNsaFJUU9TJzepErDrLITQfcmqBMo-slCbfbJQm30&h=fa787af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918228/org/56ccf1b831378fc4b3dc04d537fdb33d.jpg/Lpp9KxG7AEdfZa3q9ELvYYxhALSnvGDi5dAtfeXQLX0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918228%2Forg%2F56ccf1b831378fc4b3dc04d537fdb33d.jpg%2FLpp9KxG7AEdfZa3q9ELvYYxhALSnvGDi5dAtfeXQLX0&h=5f448698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918230/org/65571c3e59adc003b24a069cf8da2f46.jpg/crmbVOHhijdtXyBr37As7A11cJHySsifc8xTBHPMUwQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918230%2Forg%2F65571c3e59adc003b24a069cf8da2f46.jpg%2FcrmbVOHhijdtXyBr37As7A11cJHySsifc8xTBHPMUwQ&h=11882738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新劇造型曝光<br />\n<br />\n雖然李蘭迪之前亦曾經參演過古裝劇集，不過仍稱不上主演。2019年，李蘭迪終於有機會第一次穿古裝在《夢回大清》中飾演女主角茗薇。其實最初期的劇集造型出爐的時候，李蘭迪的茗薇造型並未能引起討論，但直至上星期，李蘭迪在微博展出自己的古裝照時，瞬間升級成為討論熱話，網友紛紛以「仙女下凡」來形容她的造型，更有報道指她的古裝魅力能稱得上「最美古裝女星」。與陳鈺琪和鞠婧禕不同的是，李蘭迪並不太瘦，雖然骨感欠奉但卻突顯出較為飽滿的古裝女性美態。"},{"pid":"831311005fc8f80e0eb14a42f0fa48ed395c4178","tid":1238664,"uid":173631,"like":3,"dislike":50,"score":-47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:47:12.000Z","msg":"李蘭迪顏值真係好高：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918242/org/d7606d07070ce462a92fe6a0d3339135.jpg/inrE_OpXYVZ9zogfZzDIiHEuuMizt2Okc8eh1XPHodU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918242%2Forg%2Fd7606d07070ce462a92fe6a0d3339135.jpg%2FinrE_OpXYVZ9zogfZzDIiHEuuMizt2Okc8eh1XPHodU&h=9bde38e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918239/org/fe8fde2b8d630cf9e15d6cfd5925f8fc.jpg/RhhALt49W5vpoB7npDMrGt9GNEfvvufSSJ_gDEif4Aw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918239%2Forg%2Ffe8fde2b8d630cf9e15d6cfd5925f8fc.jpg%2FRhhALt49W5vpoB7npDMrGt9GNEfvvufSSJ_gDEif4Aw&h=944f821e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918247/org/efff64f62faf579f56b7cb9299485a4e.jpg/7MZhCIq47ubkaKZhbKlhmzFFWXJ1NdbE138hTdd_IU0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918247%2Forg%2Fefff64f62faf579f56b7cb9299485a4e.jpg%2F7MZhCIq47ubkaKZhbKlhmzFFWXJ1NdbE138hTdd_IU0&h=0c45e875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918244/org/9fb59b3fd43295d9833f1ceb5a810dd3.jpg/gNaHboma3Gmg7NTgT7ZwyRAAPBeXfc3s8bhzWPG4c1g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918244%2Forg%2F9fb59b3fd43295d9833f1ceb5a810dd3.jpg%2FgNaHboma3Gmg7NTgT7ZwyRAAPBeXfc3s8bhzWPG4c1g&h=d4f37210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918237/org/bb62471833eea780309852c1f58b0c14.jpg/WNtxHBtcdUTxDdwR6lgReq9q3_nHO5Y7H-8pbB_vKWw\" data-thumbnail